    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《地府有点忙》：人间阳寿延长，阴司KPI爆表，鬼差被迫下凡冲业绩。可刚到阳间，就发现有人暗中收割阴魂、扰乱轮回！更糟的是——顶头上司钟馗竟被绑架了！一场荒诞爆笑的冥界大乱斗，就此打响！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116700/extras/b9dad18acb04419e07194147e1b94f74.poster.avif?t=1772014843\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116700/extras/b9dad18acb04419e07194147e1b94f74.webm?t=1772014843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116700/extras/b9dad18acb04419e07194147e1b94f74.mp4?t=1772014843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>千魂夜宴百鬼赴约</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在杀机暗涌的战场上，迎战如潮水般涌来的敌人，你所到之处便卷起一道死亡旋风——尽享割草般的杀戮快感吧，鬼差的快乐就是这么朴实无华。在一众鬼将中选择你的心头好，在全新的冒险中体验酣畅淋漓的杀戮盛宴~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116700/extras/534f8b0d9f5081960bdeab2ddafeaa22.poster.avif?t=1772014843\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116700/extras/534f8b0d9f5081960bdeab2ddafeaa22.webm?t=1772014843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116700/extras/534f8b0d9f5081960bdeab2ddafeaa22.mp4?t=1772014843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>招魂百式，流派自成</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人生无常，<strong>阴律</strong>莫测！自由搭配<strong>命石</strong>与阴律激发出意想不到的联动效应，并用<strong>魂币</strong>兑换通神<strong>纸扎</strong>塞爆背包，千种连招、万般杀法——没有一场战斗相同，让每次出征惊喜从不重样！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116700/extras/571b87696f40f01463721938bf55a8b4.poster.avif?t=1772014843\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116700/extras/571b87696f40f01463721938bf55a8b4.webm?t=1772014843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116700/extras/571b87696f40f01463721938bf55a8b4.mp4?t=1772014843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>文能劝架，武能镇煞</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中除了要和冥界的闹事野鬼群众物理意义上“打成一片”解决各种麻烦，还需日行一善，饿死鬼讨饭、财神丢元宝、狐仙修仙卡壳，调停阴间鸡毛蒜皮——毕竟，金牌鬼差，文能劝架，武能清场！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116700/extras/806674375df2cee5cb5cb9293e4d456a.poster.avif?t=1772014843\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116700/extras/806674375df2cee5cb5cb9293e4d456a.webm?t=1772014843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116700/extras/806674375df2cee5cb5cb9293e4d456a.mp4?t=1772014843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>展望持续更新</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏开发者致力于为玩家提供更新鲜、更有时效性、更有趣的玩法内容，我们会按照如下的开发进程，为喜欢并支持我们的玩家献上一份满意的答卷。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们十分期望聆听玩家的声音，也欢迎玩家们为我们出谋划策，将宝贵的点子分享给我们，同我们一起完善这款游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116700/extras/508c3f02507e88b4886e109634825472.poster.avif?t=1772014843\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116700/extras/508c3f02507e88b4886e109634825472.webm?t=1772014843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116700/extras/508c3f02507e88b4886e109634825472.mp4?t=1772014843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
